---
title: WOCS Phase 1 - Core Class Model (Low Level Design)
---
classDiagram
    class User {
        +UUID userId
        +String role
        +String name
        +login()
        +hasPermission()
    }
    
    class Warehouse {
        +String warehouseId
        +String type
        +boolean mandatoryLocation
        +boolean mandatorySerial
    }
    
    class InventoryItem {
        +UUID itemId
        +UUID clientId
        +String sku
        +int quantity
        +String batchLot
        +Date expiryDate
        +String storageType
        +String location
        +adjustQuantity(newVal, reason, user)
        +transfer(warehouseId)
    }
    
    class Order {
        +UUID orderId
        +UUID clientId
        +String deliveryAddress
        +String shippingMethod
        +String status
        +DateTime slaStartTime
        +DateTime dispatchTime
        +updateState(newState, user)
    }
    
    class OrderLineItem {
        +UUID lineItemId
        +String sku
        +int quantity
    }
    
    class SLAConfig {
        +UUID clientId
        +int slaDurationHours
        +String slaStartStatus
        +checkBreach(currentTime, dispatchTime)
    }
    
    class BillingRate {
        +UUID clientId
        +String warehouseId
        +String activityType
        +float rate
        +Date effectiveDate
        +calculateCharge(quantity)
    }
    
    class AuditLog {
        +UUID logId
        +UUID userId
        +DateTime timestamp
        +String action
        +String previousState
        +String newState
    }
    
    Order "1" *-- "*" OrderLineItem : contains
    Order --> SLAConfig : governed by
    InventoryItem --> AuditLog : logs to
    Order --> AuditLog : logs to
    Warehouse "1" --> "*" InventoryItem : stores
